# Membership Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

## General Membership

### What is the Remote Business Partner membership?

The Remote Business Partner membership is a platform designed to help businesses improve operations, implement systems, and access expert advisory support. Members gain access to resources such as templates, guides, AI-generated documents, partner offers, business tools, and advisory services.

### Who is the membership designed for?

The membership is designed for business owners, leaders, and managers who want to improve how their business operates. It is particularly useful for small to medium-sized businesses looking to implement systems, processes, and better decision-making frameworks.

### How do I join the membership?

You can join by selecting a membership plan on the website and completing the sign-up process. Once registered, you will gain access to the member dashboard and available resources.

### Can I upgrade my membership later?

Yes. Members can upgrade their membership at any time. When upgrading, the new plan benefits will become available immediately.

### Can I cancel my membership?

Yes. Monthly and annual memberships can be cancelled at any time. Your membership benefits will remain active until the end of the billing period.

## Membership Plans

### What membership plans are available?

The platform offers four membership options: - Basic (Free) - Lifetime (One-time payment) - Standard (Monthly or annual subscription) - Premium (Monthly or annual subscription)

### What is the difference between the plans?

Each membership tier unlocks additional features. Basic provides learning resources, Standard focuses on implementing systems, and Premium provides strategic support and additional benefits such as unlimited AI document generation and advisory advantages.

### What is the Lifetime membership?

The Lifetime membership is a one-time purchase that mirrors the Basic plan but includes limited AI document generation each month.

### What happens if I exceed my AI document limit?

If you exceed the monthly limit for AI-generated documents, you may generate additional documents for a small usage-based fee.

## DocShare

### What is DocShare?

DocShare is the platform's library of templates, tools, documentation suites, and business process resources designed to help businesses implement systems and improve operations.

### What types of resources are available in DocShare?

Resources include templates, companion guides, documentation suites, operational playbooks, process maps, tools, and industry-specific resources.

### What are documentation suites?

Documentation suites are bundles of templates and supporting materials that together form a complete system for managing a business function such as hiring, operations, or financial reporting.

### What are end-to-end processes?

End-to-end processes provide complete frameworks that outline how to manage a business function from start to finish, including documentation, workflows, and reporting structures.

### What are AI-generated documents?

Members can generate customised documents using AI by selecting a template and providing information about their business. The system will generate a tailored document that can be edited or downloaded.

## Manual Review Services

### What are manual review services?

Manual review services allow members to request expert review of documents generated through the platform or created using templates.

### What types of reviews are available?

Reviews can include AI-generated document review, template customisation review, process documentation review, and AI output quality review.

### Who can access manual review services?

Availability depends on the membership plan. Standard and Premium members receive greater access to these services.

## Partner Marketplace

### What is the Partner Marketplace?

The Partner Marketplace provides access to tools, services, and resources from trusted partners that can help improve how your business operates.

### What types of partner offers are available?

The marketplace includes partner offers, top partner offers, referral partners, exclusive member deals, and verified partner programs.

### What are exclusive partner offers?

Exclusive partner offers provide discounts or special benefits that are only available to paid members.

### What is the cashback benefit?

Premium members may receive cashback rewards when purchasing selected partner products or services through the platform.

## Knowledge Center

### What is the Knowledge Center?

The Knowledge Center contains educational resources designed to help members understand and improve different areas of their business.

### What resources are included in the Knowledge Center?

Resources include articles, guides, tools, checklists, playbooks, case studies, learning paths, business assessments, webinars, and research reports.

### Are all knowledge resources available to every member?

Some resources are available to all members, while others are reserved for Standard and Premium members.

## Services

### What advisory services are available?

Members can access advisory services across several business areas including operations, finance, sales and marketing, human resources, management, change management, and artificial intelligence.

### Do members receive discounts on services?

Yes. Members receive discounts on advisory services depending on their membership tier.

### What are discovery calls?

Discovery calls are introductory sessions where members can discuss their business challenges and determine the best way to move forward.

### What are strategic check-ups?

Strategic check-ups are periodic advisory sessions available to Premium members that focus on reviewing business performance and identifying improvement opportunities.

## Support

### What support options are available?

Support includes a help desk, onboarding support, knowledge base resources, AI document assistance, resource guidance, community discussions, office hours, and implementation support depending on the membership plan.

### What is implementation support?

Implementation support helps members apply the resources and systems provided in the platform to their own business operations.

### Do Premium members receive priority support?

Yes. Premium members receive priority responses from the support team and additional assistance with implementation.

## Billing and Payments

### What payment methods are accepted?

Payment methods depend on the payment provider used by the platform but typically include major credit cards and online payment options.

### Can I switch between monthly and annual plans?

Yes. Members can change their billing preference depending on their needs.

### Do annual memberships offer savings?

Yes. Annual memberships are offered at a discounted rate compared to paying monthly.

### Are refunds available?

Refund policies depend on the specific terms outlined during signup and may vary based on the type of membership purchased.